### Create Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "senderId": "user123",
  "recipientId": "user456",
  "description": "Payment for services"
}

### Get All Payments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments

### Get Payment by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/1

### Filter by Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments?status=PENDING

### Update Payment Status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/3/status?status=COMPLETED

### Test Validation Error
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -10,
  "currency": "US",
  "senderId": "",
  "recipientId": "user456"
}

### Test Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/999

### Delete Payment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/3